data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT BATCH, b.cusnc, b.cusnc + case when len(b.cusnc)>4 then ' 您好！' else ' 先生/女士您好！' end as mydear, a.duedat, d.comn, b.applydat, b.birthday, b.contacttel , b.mobile, b.socialid, b.email, g.codenc, b.rzone3, dateadd(d,1, a.duedat) as newBillingDat , isnull(e.cutnc, '')+ b.township2+b.raddr2 as addr2 , isnull(f.cutnc, '')+ b.township3+b.raddr3 as addr3 , I.CASEPAYD AS P01, I.CSBARCOD1 AS COD11, I.CSBARCOD2 AS COD12, I.CSBARCOD3 AS COD13, dateadd(M, I.QT_MON, a.duedat) AS D1 , I.CSNOTICEID AS CSNOTICEID01, I.CSCUSID AS CSCUSID01, I.QT_MON AS Q1 , J.CASEPAYD AS P02, J.CSBARCOD1 AS COD21, J.CSBARCOD2 AS COD22, J.CSBARCOD3 AS COD23, dateadd(M, J.QT_MON, a.duedat) AS D2 , J.CSNOTICEID AS CSNOTICEID02, J.CSCUSID AS CSCUSID02, J.QT_MON AS Q2 , K.CASEPAYD AS P03, K.CSBARCOD1 AS COD31, K.CSBARCOD2 AS COD32, K.CSBARCOD3 AS COD33, dateadd(M, K.QT_MON, a.duedat) AS D3 , K.CSNOTICEID AS CSNOTICEID03, K.CSCUSID AS CSCUSID03, K.QT_MON AS Q3, A.NOTICEID FROM RTLessorAVSCustBillingPrtSub a inner join RTLessorAVSCust b on a.comq1 = b.comq1 and a.lineq1 = b.lineq1 and a.cusid = b.cusid inner join RTLessorAVSCmtyLine c on b.comq1 = c.comq1 and b.lineq1 = c.lineq1 inner join RTLessorAVSCmtyH d on d.comq1 = c.comq1 left outer join RTCounty e on e.cutid = b.cutid2 left outer join RTCounty f on f.cutid = b.cutid3 left outer join RTCode g on g.code = b.paycycle and g.kind ='M8' left outer join RTCode h on h.code = b.casekind and h.kind ='O9' left outer join V_BARCODE I on i.NOTICEID=a.NOTICEID AND I.ITEMNO=1 left outer join V_BARCODE J on J.NOTICEID=a.NOTICEID AND J.ITEMNO=2 left outer join V_BARCODE K on K.NOTICEID=a.NOTICEID AND K.ITEMNO=3 WHERE b.freecode<>'Y' and BATCH='20180101' order by BATCH
